acceptance_criteria: "PM_GITIGNORE_BLOCK (src/sdk/workspace.ts) covers .agents/pm/transactions/, with an explicit recorded decision for .agents/pm/checkpoints/ (checkpoint-gc exists; journals have no GC at all); Documented retention policy plus gc integration prunes committed/compensated journals without breaking transactionId idempotent replay (steps are contract-idempotent, so pruned receipts only cost re-inspection); Merge-safety disposition for repos that track .agents/pm recorded with the pm-g5sx family map (journals are per-branch runtime state and would conflict on every concurrent merge)"
